          <div class="add-info-box add-info-teal">
            <div class="add-info-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 1a11 11 0 0 1 0 22 11 11 0 0 1 0-22z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Want fine art prints?</h3>
            <p>Professional prints available</p>
            <p class="offer-text">Starting at just $25</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-info">LEARN MORE</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="prices-faq">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-grid">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>How long do sessions take?</h4>
            <p>Sessions range from 30 minutes (basic) to 90 minutes (premium). You'll receive edited photos within 2 weeks.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>What if my pet is nervous?</h4>
            <p>We're experienced with all personality types. Our relaxed studio environment and treats help even shy pets feel comfortable.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Do I get digital copies?</h4>
            <p>Yes! All sessions include digital copies. You can also order professional prints in various formats and sizes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Can I reschedule?</h4>
            <p>Of course. We offer flexible rescheduling up to 48 hours before your session with no penalty.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
